graph TD
    subgraph Windows_Server [Windows Server Environment]
        WEL[Windows Event Logs] -->|Tail| LogAgent[Log Analytics Service]
        LogAgent -->|HTTP POST| MCP[MCP Server (The Brain)]
        
        subgraph Services
            LogAgent
            MCP
            SlackAg[Slack Notification Service]
        end

        MCP -->|Classify| AI[DeepSeek AI API]
        AI -->|Severity| MCP
        
        MCP --Critical/High--> SlackAg
        SlackAg -->|Webhook| Slack[Slack Workspace]
    end

    style MCP fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style AI fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
